525
00:59:30,860 --> 00:59:33,351
Uskoro ce konzulov camac
pristati uz brod.

526
00:59:33,596 --> 00:59:35,427
Budite spremni da podignete vesla.

527
00:59:41,704 --> 00:59:44,502
Podignite vesla.

528
00:59:47,009 --> 00:59:49,136
Spustite vesla.

