544
01:02:43,319 --> 01:02:47,085
Oci su ti pune mržnje, 41.

545
01:02:47,523 --> 01:02:51,687
To je dobro. Mržnja cini coveka živog.

546
01:02:51,994 --> 01:02:53,859
Daje mu snagu.

547
01:02:55,931 --> 01:02:57,558
Slušajte me svi.

548
01:02:57,967 --> 01:03:00,265
