Cudna tama...

1503
03:25:15,392 --> 03:25:17,360
...a još je dan.

1504
03:25:26,370 --> 03:25:28,497
Njegov život se završio.

1505
03:25:49,760 --> 03:25:50,988
Šta je to?

1506
03:26:00,069 --> 03:26:01,764
Cepa me.

1507
03:26:02,739 --> 03:26:04,570
Boli me.

1508
03:26:05,575 --> 03:26:07,566
I ja secam.

